flowchart TD
    A[Need a custom indicator?] --> B{Simple rotation animation?}
    B -->|Yes| C["Conform to RotateViewable\n• Set duration\n• Override draw(_:)"]
    B -->|No| D{Complex custom animation?}
    D -->|Yes| E["Implement ActivityIndicatorViewStyleable\n+ ActivityIndicatorAnimationBuildable"]
    D -->|No| F{Any existing UIView?}
    F -->|Yes| G["Pass directly to .custom(view)\nHUD manages show/hide"]

    E --> H["Use: .indicator(MyStyle())"]
    C --> I["Use: .custom(MyRotateView())"]
    G --> J["Use: .custom(myView)"]

    style C fill:#d4edda,stroke:#28a745
    style E fill:#fff3cd,stroke:#ffc107
    style G fill:#cce5ff,stroke:#007bff
    style H fill:#fff3cd,stroke:#ffc107
    style I fill:#d4edda,stroke:#28a745
    style J fill:#cce5ff,stroke:#007bff
